.IP "\(bu" 4
\&\fBincompatibilities\fR
.Sp
.Vb 1
\& \- Now HTTP::DAV requires Perl 5.6.0+ and Scalar::Util (core in 5.8.x).
.Ve
.IP "\(bu" 4
\&\fBbug fixes\fR
.Sp
.Vb 3
\& \- Now HTTP::DAV objects are correctly released from memory when
