.IP "\(bu" 4
\&\fBApache 2 mod_dav support\fR
.Sp
.Vb 1
\& \- Now works with mod_dav under Apache 2.
.Ve
.IP "\(bu" 4
\&\fBbug fixes\fR
.Sp
.Vb 1
\& \- Fixed bug to correctly handle the put/get of filenames with spaces in them.
\&
